oai_dc:dc.dc:title: FACILE SYNTHESIS OF RU4(CO)10(MU-CO)(MU-4-SE)2 AND ITS REACTIONS WITH PHOSPINE LIGANDS
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: MATHUR, P
HOSSAIN, MM
RASHID, RS
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: chalcogen carbonyl-compounds
cluster compounds
reactivity
chemistry
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The title compound has been prepared by refluxing a benzene solution containing Fe3(CO)9(mu3-Se)2 and Ru3(CO)12 or by stirring a benzene solution containing Ru3(CO)9(mu3-Se)2 and Ru(CO)4(C2H4) at room temperature. Its reactions with triphenylphosphine, bis(diphenylphosphino)methane and bis(diphenylphosphino)ethane give tetraruthenium and triruthenium phosphine derivatives.
